<TEXT>
<P>
The fourth annual citywide commemoration of the birthday of civil rights leader 
<PERSON>Dr. Martin Luther King Jr.</PERSON> will be held from <TIME>9 a.m.</TIME> to <TIME>2 p.m.</TIME> <DATE>Monday</DATE> at 
<ORGANIZATION>Robinson Park</ORGANIZATION>, <DATE>1061</DATE> <ORGANIZATION>N. Fair Oaks Ave.</ORGANIZATION> 
</P>
<P>
